    "description": "<strong>《Skábma - Snowfall》</strong>将向您展示着前所未见过的土著萨米人的故事和文化。在古老的北方篝火故事一般的世界里探索北欧之美。在这个叙事式第三人称冒险游戏里，用你的智慧来解决各种难题和挑战吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拯救你的家园！</h2><br>自附近的焦油坑发生事故后，萨米人村庄平静的生活就被打乱了。奇怪的疾病开始肆虐整片地区，影响了从土地到人和动物的方方面面。<br><br>在游戏里，你将成为<strong>Áilu</strong>，一个正在寻找逃跑驯鹿的年轻萨米牧民。当<strong>Áilu</strong>发现了被施了魔法的古老萨满鼓——“<strong>Goavddis</strong>”时，那日益蔓延的疾病的谜开始慢慢解开。感染者们的时间不多了，但萨满（<strong>Noaidis</strong>）那失传已久的医学知识仍在鼓中跳动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/0736081865e3c82d4c6051abf7c33194.poster.avif?t=1748596518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/0736081865e3c82d4c6051abf7c33194.webm?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/0736081865e3c82d4c6051abf7c33194.mp4?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你总能找回失去的东西！找到四个使魔，重建与大自然的连接，并找到疾病的源头。你是时候成为新时代的萨满（<strong>Noaidis</strong>）了！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特征</h2><br><strong>故事导向</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/c59081903689cf66ba389eb5fe20ed59.poster.avif?t=1748596518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/c59081903689cf66ba389eb5fe20ed59.webm?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/c59081903689cf66ba389eb5fe20ed59.mp4?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>关于欧洲最后的土著民族萨米人的独特故事。感受北方萨米人全语音的过场动画，沉浸在叙事式的冒险故事里。 <br><br><strong>使魔 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/04d8c027b97b4e3ff3e79216461ab87f.poster.avif?t=1748596518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/04d8c027b97b4e3ff3e79216461ab87f.webm?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/04d8c027b97b4e3ff3e79216461ab87f.mp4?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>找到四个使魔：猫头鹰“<strong>Skuolfi</strong>”，熊“<strong>Guovža</strong>”，鳟鱼“<strong>Čámsa</strong>”和狐狸“<strong>Rieban</strong>”。他们以不同的力量影响着你的行动和调节传播在萨米大地的疾病的能力。  <br><br><strong>鼓声与冒险 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/7dbc0b488653d299dbca57dea4864fc0.poster.avif?t=1748596518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/7dbc0b488653d299dbca57dea4864fc0.webm?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/7dbc0b488653d299dbca57dea4864fc0.mp4?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用你的萨满鼓和使魔的力量来揭露北极自然中看不见的元素。跟随通往收藏品、人的灵魂和树木精灵的踪迹，它们将会帮助你通过障碍、以及解开挡在面前的各种谜题。 <br><br><strong>沉浸式北部世界 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/40a5b48c1bb7fec2780d4b3a3f6a2545.poster.avif?t=1748596518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/40a5b48c1bb7fec2780d4b3a3f6a2545.webm?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/40a5b48c1bb7fec2780d4b3a3f6a2545.mp4?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沉浸在由获奖的民谣歌团“<strong>Hildá Länsman</strong>”等带来的传统萨米歌谣的同时，探索现实世界和精神世界的神秘风景。探索<strong>Áilu</strong>的世界，并找到祖父的家族宝藏和外人对萨米文化看法的记录，捉野兔并和妖精交谈，以更了解游戏世界和萨米故事。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/1a2b4752a64d74badc9c5fa327fbd323.poster.avif?t=1748596518\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/1a2b4752a64d74badc9c5fa327fbd323.webm?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1665280/extras/1a2b4752a64d74badc9c5fa327fbd323.mp4?t=1748596518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>跳入一场穿越荒野和精神世界的冒险吧！",
